---
import LoanProductLayout from "@/layouts/LoanProductLayout.astro";
const title = "Working capital finance";
const subtitle = "Keep your business moving. Cover everyday costs, payroll, inventory, invoices without disrupting cash flow. Compare options from multiple lenders and find flexible funding in minutes.";
---
<LoanProductLayout title={title} subtitle={subtitle} updatedAt="November 2025">
  
  <!-- What is working capital finance -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">What is working capital finance?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Working capital finance is a type of funding designed to cover short-term business needs. Instead of using it for long-term investments like property or machinery, it's used to bridge gaps in everyday cash flow.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed">
      It helps businesses pay bills, staff, and suppliers, even when payments from customers are delayed. It can also support seasonal fluctuations or provide a buffer for unexpected costs.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-6">How does working capital finance work?</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-black text-lg">Lender approval</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">A lender approves a facility such as a business loan, invoice finance, or revolving credit facility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-black text-lg">Access funds</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">You access the funds when required – either as a lump sum or flexible drawdowns.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-black text-lg">Repay over term</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Repayments are made over an agreed term, usually with interest and fees.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold">4</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-black text-lg">Continue trading</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Once repaid, you continue trading without disruption to your working capital cycle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Types of working capital finance -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Types of working capital finance</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Short-term loans</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Flexible borrowing for cash flow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Invoice finance</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Release money tied up in unpaid invoices.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Revolving credit facility</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Draw down funds when needed, repay, and re-borrow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Merchant cash advance</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Borrow against future card sales.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Asset finance</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Fund vehicles, machinery and assets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white hover:border-lime-300 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Overdrafts</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Flexible but often with lower limits.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Is it right for your business -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Is working capital finance right for your business?</h2>
    
    <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-3">€100k–€5m turnover</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">
          You might need working capital finance if you have seasonal sales, wait 30+ days for customer payments, need to purchase stock before busy periods, or currently use personal funds for business expenses.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-3">€5m+ turnover</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">
          You could need working capital finance if you're comparing costs against existing credit lines, need faster access than traditional banking, or want to diversify your sources of funding.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-3">When it makes sense</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-4">
        Working capital finance can make sense when you have temporary cash flow gaps rather than fundamental profitability issues.
      </p>
      <p class="text-neutral-700">
        For example, a €3 million catering business might need €150k for a large event contract, while a €15 million distribution company could use €800k to take advantage of bulk purchase discounts from suppliers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Benefits -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Benefits of working capital finance</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Pros</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Smooths cash flow gaps</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Keeps suppliers and staff paid on time</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Flexible options from loans to invoice finance</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Often quicker to arrange than equity or long-term loans</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-lime-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Helps seize growth opportunities</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-4">Cons</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Short-term cost can be higher than long-term loans</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">May require collateral or personal guarantees</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Over-borrowing can strain future cash flow</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Not designed for major investments</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded bg-neutral-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-neutral-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4.293 4.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 8.586l4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414L11.414 10l4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414 1.414L10 11.414l-4.293 4.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L8.586 10 4.293 5.707a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="text-neutral-700">Interest and fees vary by product</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- How Runway works -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">How does Runway work?</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Tell us how much you need</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">We'll ask a few questions about your business and the reason for your loan.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Get quotes instantly</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">Our smart technology will compare quotes from multiple lenders to help you find the ideal business loan.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white text-center">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-lime-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <span class="text-lime-900 font-semibold text-xl">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Apply for a Business Loan</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 text-sm">We'll be there to guide you through every step of the process.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-3xl md:text-4xl text-black mb-8">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Is working capital finance secured or unsecured?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">It depends on the product. Loans can be unsecured, while invoice finance and asset refinance use business assets as security.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">How much can I borrow?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">This depends on turnover, credit profile and product type. Facilities can range from €5,000 to millions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">How quickly can I access funds?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Some facilities, like invoice finance or revolving credit, can be set up in 24–48 hours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Is it suitable for startups?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">It can be more difficult for startups without trading history, but some lenders may consider them.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">What's the difference between working capital finance and a business loan?</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-700">Working capital finance is short-term funding to cover day-to-day needs. Business loans can also fund longer-term investments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Disclaimer -->
  <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-zinc-50">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-4">
      <strong class="text-black">Important:</strong> Please note that the information above is not intended to be financial advice. You should seek independent financial advice before making any decisions about your financial future.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700 mb-4">
      It's important to remember that all loans and credit agreements come with risks. These risks include non-payment and late-payment of the agreed repayment plan, which could affect your business credit score and impact your ability to find future funding. Always read the terms and conditions of every loan or credit agreement before you proceed.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
      Runway helps businesses access business finance, working directly with businesses and their trusted advisors. Runway is a credit broker and does not provide loans directly. All finance and quotes are subject to status and income. Applicants must be aged 18 and over and terms and conditions apply.
    </p>
  </div>

</LoanProductLayout>
